{"tid":730420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前港大學生會爭議會長陳冠康 考入政府做AO","createTime":"2018-07-05T11:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T16:44:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ea5169d5207d8da51b802fed3c57aee3a573d0","tid":730420,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/193726_12c8669cfaff7de08512a9b3955cd5bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F193726_12c8669cfaff7de08512a9b3955cd5bb.png&h=cc6fbdd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年不時有大專學界嘅學生會被指染紅，好似2012年接任港大學生會會長嘅陳冠康，曾經面臨下台壓力。2013年就有逾千名港大學生喺年初集會，抗議周年大會黑箱作業，又質疑學生會染紅，要求會長陳冠康等人下台，陳冠康則曾發聲明反擊，話校園媒體同本港傳媒中傷同抹黑佢嘅「愛國之心」，有人將校園變得政治化。<br />\n<br />\n事隔幾年，陳冠康嘅名字再度出現，但今次唔係捲入學界紛爭，而係佢已經搖身一變入咗政府做AO。探子回報，陳冠康已經喺上月28日履新，喺食物及衞生局做助理秘書長(衞生)。據知佢2014年港大畢業後攞過Chevening獎學金，去咗倫敦大學學院（UCL）修讀全球公共政策碩士課程，之後喺不同大型及國際機構工作過，如今考入政府做政務官，唔通都係覺得「鐵飯碗」吸引啲？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58402290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402290&d=wz%2FZjKwIRaCioXb8dQfv8W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=64bcd26f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402290&h=dfa3352d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58402290</a>"},{"pid":"71c480c2df4f5920a6d83daed170f99d354e9e4d","tid":730420,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"講真，香港係需要啲咁嘅人"},{"pid":"8050f6771db260ec59cdd2fc297a02c70962543c","tid":730420,"uid":3241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"賤人， 佢去到邊部門都投撚訴佢"},{"pid":"86414e3a34d271be0bc0770cd9355955c7cb5fc6","tid":730420,"uid":4258,"like":1,"dislike":8